headline: 4Rivers Equipment Named Newest Trimble Technology Outlet
summary: Trimble® today announced Greeley, Colorado-based 4Rivers Equipment as the newest Trimble Technology Outlet. 4Rivers will now sell Trimble grade control, site positioning systems and correction services technology directly to customers using John Deere construction equipment.
